<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP21_ProjectGold_FamilyTree_Forgery" s="489344">
  <T n="category">488441<!--TutorialCategory: tutorial_Category_EP21_ProjectGold--></T>
  <T n="name">0xE497DEC8<!--String: "Forging Connections"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_FamilyTree_Forgery1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:99c3f838db8c34ae</T>
      <T n="text">0xA768AB29<!--String: "Ever felt like taking a shortcut in your pursuit of power? Now you can <b><font color='#199C2C'>Forge a fake family connection</font></b> between a Sim in your family (including yourself) and someone completely unrelated. Even a Noble!\n\nAll other Sims will treat the two as if they were truly related in all aspects of daily life, including the ability to join the same Dynasty.\n\nTo do this, acquire the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Family Tree Tapestry</font></b> in <b><font color='#199C2C'>Build Mode</font></b>. Return to Live Mode and select <b><font color='#199C2C'>Forge Family Tree</font></b> on the Family Tree Tapestry."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_FamilyTree_Forgery2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:99c3f838db8c34ad</T>
      <T n="text">0xBD71A9B8<!--String: "Pick two Sims you want to connect, and choose what type of relatives they shall be. Some options will not always be available, as they might require a <b><font color='#199C2C'>not-fake relative</font></b> in between to connect them.\n\nSome examples: when forging a connection between a fake grandparent and their fake grandchild, you'll need to ensure there's a <b><font color='#199C2C'>parent</font></b> in between to link them.\nWhen forging a connection between two <b><font color='#199C2C'>fake siblings</font></b>, you'll need to ensure that either of them has at least one real parent: this parent will become the new <b><font color='#199C2C'>fake parent</font></b> of the other sibling.\n\nAdditionally, when forging a fake parent, they will need to be <b><font color='#199C2C'>older</font></b> than their fake child.\nForged connections are not possible between two families where any members are in a <b><font color='#199C2C'>romance</font></b> with the other family."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="tags">
    <E>Lesson_EP21_ProjectGold_FamilyTree</E>
  </L>
